<h1 class="docs-header">Media Query Variables</h1>
<p>Where media query breakpoints and breakpoint features are defined. These are used in the core media file for the media queries.</p>

<ul class="variables">
  
  <li class="title">Breakpoints</li>
  <li><code>$bp-small</code> <code class="value">480px</code></li>
  <li><code>$bp-mobile</code> <code class="value">760px</code></li>
  <li><code>$bp-tablet</code> <code class="value">760px</code></li>
  <li><code>$bp-desktop</code> <code class="value">990px</code></li>
  <li><code>$bp-large</code> <code class="value">1380px</code></li>

  <li class="title">Features</li>
  <li><code>$bp-small-feature</code> <code class="value">max-width</code></li>
  <li><code>$bp-mobile-feature</code> <code class="value">max-width</code></li>
  <li><code>$bp-tablet-feature</code> <code class="value">min-width</code></li>
  <li><code>$bp-desktop-feature</code> <code class="value">min-width</code></li>
  <li><code>$bp-large-feature</code> <code class="value">min-width</code></li>

</ul>
